# ===== Root .gitignore (cool-bath monorepo) =====

.DS_Store
node_modules/

# ---- Secrets / SDK (TUYỆT ĐỐI KHÔNG commit) ----
# Keys + SDK do client cấp
docs/sdk/keys.txt
docs/sdk/**/*.zip
docs/sdk/**/*.tar.gz
docs/sdk/Android_SDK/
docs/sdk/iOS_SDK/

# env (chỉ commit *.example)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Tuya security files (binary, per-app)
**/security-algorithm*.aar
**/ios_core_sdk.tar.gz
**/ThingSmartCryption*
packages/tuya-react-native/example/ios/Build/
packages/tuya-react-native/example/android/app/libs/

# build outputs
**/dist/
**/lib/
**/.next/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# LƯU Ý: example/android/gradle.properties hiện chứa THING_SMART_APPKEY/SECRET (dev).
# Trước khi commit, chuyển 2 key đó sang ~/.gradle/gradle.properties (global, ngoài repo).
